### Issue 4: Arbitrary File Read via OrchestrationPath/McpPath

Validate paths against an allowed base directory:

```csharp
// Add helper after allowedBrowseDirs
static bool IsPathAllowed(string path, string[] allowedBases)
{
    var fullPath = Path.GetFullPath(path);
    return allowedBases.Any(allowed =>
        fullPath.StartsWith(allowed + Path.DirectorySeparatorChar, StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase));
}

// In /api/load, add validation after line 43:
if (!IsPathAllowed(request.OrchestrationPath, allowedBrowseDirs))
    return Results.BadRequest(new { error = "Orchestration path is not within allowed directories." });

// And for McpPath after line 50:
if (!IsPathAllowed(request.McpPath, allowedBrowseDirs))
    return Results.BadRequest(new { error = "MCP path is not within allowed directories." });
```

