### Issue 6: Inconsistent Indentation

Fix line 166 — change leading space to tab:

```csharp
// Before (line 166):
    await httpContext.Response.WriteAsync($"data: {executionStartedJson}\n\n");

// After:
	await httpContext.Response.WriteAsync($"data: {executionStartedJson}\n\n");
```

