### Issue 7: Task Exception Handling

Handle exceptions from the background task explicitly:

```csharp
// After line 259, replace simple await with:
try
{
    await executionTask;
}
catch (Exception ex)
{
    // Log if needed, but don't fail - execution errors already reported via SSE
    var logger = loggerFactory.CreateLogger("Execution");
    logger.LogWarning(ex, "Execution task ended with exception");
}
```

